{"tid":1017452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留下啤酒遺書　男子城門水塘上吊亡","createTime":"2019-02-11T12:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T13:05:02.000Z","uid":160807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"58fcffefbe642a4c880be97272cf987088fe19d1","tid":1017452,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190211/large/1549851773_8afa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190211%2Flarge%2F1549851773_8afa.jpg&h=a01c3949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上約7時半，一名男子，被行山人士發現於荃灣城門水塘近蝴蝶園，用繩在一個木架上吊。救護員趕到將他解下，經檢驗證實事主已告不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方大範圍封鎖現場進行調查，並在場撿獲數頁紙的遺書、一打啤酒罐，香煙以及一個藍色背囊，相信是姓林(48歲)男死者遺下；初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。據悉，死者受癌症困擾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190211/59245396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59245396&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu10cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=70e84a0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59245396&h=3b76c39f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190211/59245396</a>"},{"pid":"d0136cea43f352602188b275696a63ef12cd6243","tid":1017452,"uid":152262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:41:03.000Z","msg":"行山見到真係得人驚"},{"pid":"126d4a4e75f2d25d7e0a27a1f5cfac5e1af0f49c","tid":1017452,"uid":121546,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"上吊(48歲)"},{"pid":"a87a3f21f221d10d11f92ccffa3858235babd3b7","tid":1017452,"uid":202354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:54:07.000Z","msg":"屌,我成日經城門水塘行上大帽山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/l